" Mapping (Bundle) Settings


" Rapidly these keys (instead of Esc) to go Normal mode.
inoremap jk <Esc>
inoremap kj <Esc>

" When wrapping is enabled, move down by row not by line.
nnoremap j gj
nnoremap k gk

" Sublime-style autoindent
imap {<CR> {<CR>}<C-o>O

" Change leader to something saner.
"let mapleader=","
